## Hexagonal Architecture - Verification Checklist

After each feature, verify these principles:

### ‚úÖ Domain Layer (src/domain/)
- [ ] NO imports from Next.js, React, Octokit, or any framework
- [ ] All models are pure TypeScript classes/interfaces
- [ ] All services are pure static functions
- [ ] Domain tests require NO mocking

### ‚úÖ Use Case Layer (src/usecase/)
- [ ] Depends ONLY on domain ports (interfaces)
- [ ] NO concrete infrastructure implementations
- [ ] Tests use mocked ports only
- [ ] Framework-agnostic orchestration

### ‚úÖ Infrastructure Layer (src/infrastructure/)
- [ ] Implements all domain ports
- [ ] All framework-specific code here
- [ ] Converts external DTOs to domain models
- [ ] Integration tests mock external APIs

### ‚úÖ API Routes (app/api/)
- [ ] Thin controllers with dependency injection
- [ ] Wire up: Infrastructure ‚Üí Use Cases
- [ ] NO business logic in routes
- [ ] Handle HTTP concerns only

### ‚úÖ Presentation Layer (components/)
- [ ] Consume API endpoints
- [ ] Display domain model data
- [ ] NO business logic in components
- [ ] Formatting is presentational only

